title: Jock Campbell (rugby union)
text: Jock Campbell (born 17 May 1995, in <a href="Australia">Australia</a>) is an <a href="Australian">Australian</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who plays for the <a href="Queensland%20Reds">Queensland Reds</a> in <a href="Super%20Rugby">Super Rugby</a>. His playing position is <a href="Wing%20%28rugby%20union%29">wing</a>. He has signed for the Reds in 2020.
